(2, '13878', '2019-10-09 04:42:32', '2015', 'Comedy, Parody, Seinen, Sci-Fi', '<p> The story of a bald superhero who destroys any monster with one hit. A horde of monsters fell upon our earthly world. They destroy cities, kill a large number of people. Here heroes appear, the saviors of our world. They are distributed in strength in the \"Association of Heroes\" and they correspond to their rank, someone rises, and someone remains in place. Sapama - used to be an ordinary person, he lost his job and decided to become a hero. He trained every day with grueling workouts. Now he is a real super hero. Just do not pay attention that he is bald and not really like a campaign for a real hero. In fact, he kills any monster with just one blow, which makes him bored. There are no worthy opponents. </p> <p> One fine day, our main character, Saitama, meets a man half the Genos robot. He saw the real strength of Saitama, was so shocked. He decided to become his student and learns everything. Let\'s see what happens, what interesting adventures await our heroes. </p>', '/image/OnePunchMan.jpg', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=1#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 1</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=2#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 2</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=3#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 3</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=4#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 4</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=5#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 5</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=OnePunchMan&chapter=embed/13878/&season=1&seria=6#videoPlayer\"><but