(4, '9488', '2019-10-09 04:42:32', '2003, 2004', 'Action, War, Drama, Comedy, Adventure, Shonen, Fantasy, Multi-Series', '<p> Legends about the philosopher''s stone have been around for a very long time and it says that with the help of this very stone you can create an elixir of life and turn absolutely any metal into gold. Alchemists spend a lot of time, money and resources searching. Someone needs it for wealth, and someone wants eternal life. In any case, this same "pebble" can be used not only for this. The legend also says that he is able to violate all the boundaries of alchemy, and since you can’t get something using alchemy without sacrificing something of equal value, you yourself understand the importance of discovering this very stone, if it exists at all. Bring a person back to life with an ordinary pebble ... Why not? This is what our main characters tried to do and paid a lot for it. </p> <p> Edward and Alphonse Elrica paid for their act. It was a normal desire for children to bring their deceased mother back to life, but they did not take into account the very law of alchemy. So just they did not get off. As a result of the “return” from the failed ritual, Edward lost his arm and leg, and Alfons’s soul was saved only by sealing in metal armor. Years passed, Edward passed the state exam for the alchemist, where he gets the very unusual nickname “Fullmetal Alchemist” just after that and they begin with his brother the search for this very philosopher’s stone and return what they lost in childhood and it’s not only their mother’s business in their pride. </p>', '/image/Fullmetal Alchemist.jpg', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Fullmetal Alchemist&chapter=embed/9488/&season=1&seria=1#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Film 1</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Fullmetal Alchemist&chapter=embed/9488/&season=1&seria=2#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Film 2</button></a>', 'Fullmetal Alchemist', 'Абэ Нориюки', 1, 1, 16),
(5, '9302', '2019-10-09 04:42:33', '2013', 'War, Drama, Post-apocalyptic, Adventure, Shonen, Fantasy', '<p> Boy Erin wakes up. He had a nightmare in which he saw giants and a lot of blood. There are tears on his face. Erin asks his girlfriend not to tell anyone that he was crying. The village where the heroes live is surrounded by a protective wall. Security at the gate drinks alcohol. Unhappy with this depressing picture, Erin asks his friend the guard: \"How will you fight drunk?\" He wonders: “And when will we fight?” Erin yells at the guard: “When ?! Are you still asking? When they break through our wall and burst here! ” The drunken guards chuckle at the boy, they say, we will do our job even if they burst here. </p> <p> Meanwhile, the giants loitering along the fifty-meter wall, and the head of the guard is sure that everything is in order. Erin seriously thinks about joining the Legion of Intelligence, and only the girl discourages him. The bell rings. This legion of heroes returns from intelligence. Erin hurries to see his idols. Locals surround the arrived heroes. Those bloodied ones return home, drooping their heads down dumbly. The Legion returned with heavy losses. Giants eat people alive and soon Erin will see with their own eyes how they will eat his mother. Erin will have to fight for the salvation of her people. </p>', '/image/Attack On Titan.jpg', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Attack On Titan&chapter=embed/9302/&season=1&seria=1#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 1</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Attack On Titan&chapter=embed/9302/&season=1&seria=2#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 2</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Attack On Titan&chapter=embed/9302/&season=1&seria=3#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 3</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Attack On Titan&chapter=embed/9302/&season=1&seria=4#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"b