(6, '9481', '2019-10-09 04:42:32', '2002', 'Martial Arts, Comedy, Adventure, Shonen, Fantasy, Multi-Series', '<p> Two and a half years have passed since Naruto, along with Jiraiya, left Konoha for training, traveling and searching for information about Orochimaru\'s lair and Sasuke’s whereabouts. </p>\r\n<p> Naruto was very mature, gained invaluable experience, and perhaps even learned more than one powerful technique. </p>\r\n<p> But his peers did not lag behind. The teams of Guy, Asuma and Kurenai improved their techniques and became much stronger and more cohesive. And Sakura generally exceeded all expectations. All this time, she borrowed the most sophisticated medical techniques from Tsunade, but she did not stop at them. </p>\r\n<p> Well, it\'s time to go to Sasuke\'s rescue and finally bring him back to the village. </p>\r\n<p> But on the way of the heroes, troubles again arise. The Village Hidden in the Sands was attacked by attackers, and everything indicates that they are participants in the Akatsuki. </p>\r\n<p> Kakashi’s team goes to help old friends, hoping not only to defeat the villains, but also to get some clues about Orochimaru from them so that Sasuke can be returned home. </p>', '/image/Naruto hurricane chronicles.jpg', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Naruto hurricane chronicles&chapter=embed/9481/&season=1&seria=1#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 1</button></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Naruto hurricane chronicles&chapter=embed/9481/&season=1&seria=2#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 2</button></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Naruto hurricane chronicles&chapter=embed/9481/&season=1&seria=3#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 3</button></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Naruto hurricane chronicles&chapter=embed/9481/&season=1&seria=4#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series 4</button></a>\r\n<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/hom