(8, '15341', '2019-10-09 04:42:32', '2017', 'Comedy, Adventure, Shonen, Fantasy, Multi-Series, New', '<p> A very emotional guy named Aster lives in a church. He is an orphan and was found on the doorstep of the church. He is a very active boy and dreams of the title of magician king, so that he can then rebuild his old church. Unlike everyone else, he absolutely cannot use magic, but he does not consider this an obstacle and tries to become stronger than any of his peers. His whole life consists of training and convincing himself that he will soon succeed in becoming the king of magic. One of Aster’s closest people is his clever brother Yuna. He was also thrown to the door of the church and from a very young age was distinguished by a calm disposition. </p> <p> When all the boys who dreamed of the glory of the magician in their country were given the grenoirs (special magic books) to Aster, he did not get it. But Yuna got something that no one even dared to dream about - a magical black clover. Aster was very upset that he did not become the chosen one, but did not give up, but only began to train more and strive for his goal. All the others, too, were not happy that Yuna, being an orphan and not known from what kind, received clover. According to these magicians, he is not worthy of a four-leaf clover. But Yuna doesn\'t think so. True, now he can forget about calm. On the same day that the clover was in the hands of Yuna, he appeared new enemies who wanted to take away the clover. And Aster, without any fear, began to fight for this magical attribute. By joining forces, the brothers were able to show what they are capable of. As it turns out later, their adventures are just beginning ... </p>', '/image/Black Clover.jpg', '<a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Black Clover there&chapter=embed/15341/&season=1&seria=1#videoPlayer\"><button class=\"bp-q\"> Series1</button></a><a href=\"http://localhost:8080/home/anime?page=Black Clover there&chapter=embed/153