(9, '13851', '2019-10-09 04:42:32', '2015', 'War, Harem, Comedy, Adventure, Seinen, Fantasy', '<p> In Japan, in the 21st Century, Gates appeared in the center of Ginza, leading to a parallel world. And well, they would just have appeared and the matter was over, the study of the gates, the transfer of scientists, the deployment of laboratories for the same study of these same gates would begin. Of course, everything would be quiet and peaceful because the Japanese do not like to fight. If the “guests” knew this from the other side of the gate, they would not have sent a whole army into battle, which consists not only of ordinary people. Hordes of monsters, which include not only orcs and ogres, but also wyverns and God knows what other creatures. It’s almost impossible for ordinary police units to cope with them, then the Japanese Self-Defense Forces enter the battle. Yes, Japan does not officially have an army, but this does not prevent it from having its own Self-Defense Forces. The difference in strength immediately became apparent and uninvited guests were immediately pushed back to where they came from. </p> <p> After some discussions, it was decided to send an intelligence expedition consisting mainly of soldiers to the gate. It is understandable, no one wants a repetition of events in the center of Ginza that claimed a lot of lives and who knows how many more people were captured. One of these same scouts is our main character. His name is Itami Yuji and he is an officer in the Japan Self-Defense Forces. He is 33 years old and he is Otaku. Despite his passion, thanks to his skills as an officer, he was able to prevent many deaths during the opening of the very same gate. The man’s usual campaign for the new Manga turned out to be a promotion for him and the appointment of one of the detachment commanders for reconnaissance of new territories. Meanwhile, behind the scenes, a serious political struggle begins, not only for the resources of the new world, but al